%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%88%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.5 HelloWorld案例常见问题（理解）</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-5-1-BUG\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.5.1 BUG</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-5-2-BUG%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.5.2 BUG的解决</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-5-3-HelloWorld%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.5.3 HelloWorld案例常见问题 :</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-6-Notepad-%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.6 Notepad++软件的安装和使用（应用）</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-6-1-%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Notepad-%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.6.1 什么要使用Notepad++软件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-6-2-Notepad-%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.6.2 Notepad++软件安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-6-3Notepad-%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.6.3Notepad++软件配置</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-Java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. Java基础语法</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-1-%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%EF%BC%88%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.1 注释（理解）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-2-%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%EF%BC%88%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.2 关键字（理解）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-3-%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.3 常量（应用）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-4-%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D-%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.4 变量的介绍(理解)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-5-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.5 数据类型（应用）</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-5-1-%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.5.1 计算机存储单元</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-5-2-Java%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.5.2 Java中的数据类型</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-6-%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.6 变量（应用）</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-6-1-%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.6.1 变量的定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-6-2-%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.6.2 变量的修改</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-7-%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9-%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.7 变量的注意事项(理解)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-8-%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98%E5%BD%95%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%88%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.8 键盘录入（理解）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-